In specification V2 [3]

   - a deadlock exists for rendez-vous:
        exit
     synchronized by parallel operator ``|[exit, SND_L]|''
     this gate/offer combination is used in the left operand:
        EMERGENCY_STOP [exit, DEVIATION_DETECTED, SND_L]
     but not in the right operand:
        CHANNEL_L [exit, SND_L, L_RCV]
